// segment_arena_backing_modeled_allocation_ledger_release_recycle_execution_support_requirement_matrix_box.hako -- MIMAP-328A
// Responsibility:
// - record a model-only requirement matrix for future release/recycle execution
//   support from the closed support gate facts
// - keep every real execution requirement explicit and unsatisfied
// Non-responsibility:
// - satisfying requirements, executing real release/recycle, lifecycle
//   generation, pointer residence, segment-map mutation, atomic bitmap
//   execution, OSVM calls, scheduling, providers, or backend shortcuts

